Run Server --> Create server & listen the incoming request.
Bussines logic --> Handle requests, validate Input, Connect to Database.
Response --> Return responses(Rendered HTML, JSON...).
NodeJS project steps:-

Create server using express, nodemon, body-parser.

Crete EJS template(HTML Template) for user interaction.

Routing between files and folders

Make MVC architecture( model, view, controller) model help to maintain Data like fetch , save etc view is used for templates and decoupled from your application code. controller connecting models to view and contain in-between logic.

Create Databse using Mongo-DB(Mongoose) Atlas.
